          <title>TikTok's Last Chance: Supreme Court to Hear App Ban Appeal</title>
          <description><![CDATA[TikTok's impending ban on US soil gets a last-minute reprieve as the Supreme Court agrees to hear the social media company's appeal against a federal law that could see it banned by January 19.]]></description>
